## Get Geolocation
window.navigator.geolocation.getCurrentPosition(
    position => console.log(position),
    error => console.log(error)
  );
callback won't run before the creator function returns

State:
 must be intialized when component is created
 can only be updated by setState

setState({key:value}) won't delete anything from the state, merge or add new states into the original initial values
Initial state inside constructor or instance creation in the class body
class{
state={}
constructor(props){
    super(props)
    this.state={}
    }
}
props, 
Component.defaultProps={key:value} to add a default message for props if no value is given


